<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Contrat #{{ contrat.id }}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: DejaVu Sans, sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #0c1f3f;
            background: #ffffff;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* ── Header ── */
        .header { background-color: #081533; color: #ffffff; padding: 0; }
        .header-inner { padding: 24px 32px 20px; display: table; width: 100%; }
        .header-left  { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; width: 55%; }
        .header-right { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; width: 45%; }
        .logo-wrap  { display: table; }
        .logo-img   { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; }
        .logo-img img { width: 48px; height: 48px; }
        .logo-text  { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; padding-left: 12px; }
        .brand-name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 2px; }
        .brand-sub  { font-size: 9px; color: #93c5fd; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 2px; }
        .report-label { font-size: 11px; color: #93c5fd; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .report-title { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .ref-badge {
            display: inline-block; background: #2156d8; color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .header-bar { height: 4px; background-color: #2156d8; }

        /* ── Status banner ── */
        .status-banner {
            background: #f0f5ff;
            border-left: 5px solid #2156d8;
            padding: 10px 32px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .status-banner-left  { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; width: 70%; }
        .status-banner-right { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; width: 30%; }
        .status-banner-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #0c1f3f; }
        .status-banner-sub   { font-size: 9.5px; color: #64748b; margin-top: 2px; }

        /* ── Content ── */
        .content { padding: 22px 32px; }

        /* ── Section title ── */
        .section-title {
            font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: #0c1f3f;
            border-left: 4px solid #2156d8; padding-left: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 22px;
        }
        .section-title:first-child { margin-top: 0; }

        /* ── Two-column grid ── */
        .two-col { display: table; width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 12px 0; }
        .col     { display: table-cell; vertical-align: top; width: 50%; }

        /* ── Info table ── */
        .info-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .info-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(16,24,40,.08); }
        .info-table td {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(16,24,40,.08);
            padding: 8px 12px; vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .info-table td.lbl {
            width: 42%; background: #f8fbff; font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.6px; color: #64748b;
        }
        .info-table td.val { color: #0c1f3f; font-size: 11px; }

        /* ── Badges ── */
        .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
        .b-blue   { background: #e8f0ff; color: #2156d8; }
        .b-green  { background: #e8fbf3; color: #0f8f62; }
        .b-orange { background: #fff4e5; color: #c06a00; }
        .b-red    { background: #ffe8e8; color: #b42318; }
        .b-gray   { background: #e2e8f0; color: #334155; }

        /* ── Highlight box ── */
        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f5ff 0%, #e8f0ff 100%);
            border: 1px solid #c7d9ff; border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 14px 16px; margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .highlight-box .amount {
            font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #2156d8; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .highlight-box .amount-label { font-size: 9px; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 2px; }

        /* ── Avantages box ── */
        .text-box {
            background: #f8fbff; border: 1px solid rgba(16,24,40,.08);
            border-left: 4px solid #2156d8; padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0; font-size: 10.5px;
            color: #0c1f3f; line-height: 1.7; white-space: pre-wrap;
        }

        /* ── Divider ── */
        .divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(16,24,40,.08); margin: 18px 0; }

        /* ── Signature section ── */
        .sig-section { margin-top: 28px; }
        .sig-table { display: table; width: 100%; }
        .sig-col   { display: table-cell; width: 48%; vertical-align: top; }
        .sig-spacer { display: table-cell; width: 4%; }
        .sig-box {
            border: 1px solid #d1daf5; border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 16px; background: #fafbff;
        }
        .sig-title { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .sig-name  { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #0c1f3f; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .sig-role  { font-size: 9.5px; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .sig-line  { border-top: 1.5px solid #2156d8; margin-top: 8px; padding-top: 6px; font-size: 9px; color: #94a3b8; }
        .sig-notice {
            margin-top: 14px; padding: 10px 12px;
            background: #fffbeb; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 9.5px; color: #92400e; line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* ── Footer ── */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 28px; padding: 14px 32px;
            background: #f8fbff; border-top: 1px solid rgba(16,24,40,.08);
            display: table; width: 100%;
        }
        .footer-left  { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; width: 50%; font-size: 9px; color: #64748b; }
        .footer-right { display: table-cell; vertical-align: middle; text-align: right; width: 50%; font-size: 9px; color: #64748b; }
        .footer-brand { font-weight: 700; color: #2156d8; font-size: 11px; }
        .confidential {
            display: inline-block; border: 1px solid #2156d8; color: #2156d8;
            font-size: 8px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 8px;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px; border-radius: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* ── Status helpers ── */
        {% set s = (contrat.status ?? '')|lower %}
        {% if 'actif' in s or 'active' in s %}
        {% elseif 'termin' in s or 'closed' in s %}
        {% endif %}
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══ HEADER ══ -->
<div class="header">
    <div class="header-inner">
        <div class="header-left">
            <div class="logo-wrap">
                {% if logoBase64 %}
                <div class="logo-img"><img src="{{ logoBase64 }}" alt="VOS"></div>
                {% endif %}
                <div class="logo-text">
                    <div class="brand-name">VOS</div>
                    <div class="brand-sub">Virtual Onboarding System</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="header-right">
            <div class="report-label">Document officiel</div>
            <div class="report-title">Contrat d'Embauche</div>
            <div class="ref-badge">REF #{{ contrat.id }}</div>
            <div style="margin-top:6px;font-size:9px;color:#93c5fd;">
                Genere le {{ generatedAt|date('d/m/Y') }} a {{ generatedAt|date('H:i') }}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="header-bar"></div>

<!-- ══ STATUS BANNER ══ -->
{% set statusRaw = (contrat.status ?? '')|lower %}
{% if 'actif' in statusRaw or 'active' in statusRaw %}
    {% set statusBadge = '<span class="badge b-green">' ~ (contrat.status ?? 'Actif') ~ '</span>' %}
{% elseif 'termin' in statusRaw or 'closed' in statusRaw %}
    {% set statusBadge = '<span class="badge b-red">' ~ (contrat.status ?? 'Terminé') ~ '</span>' %}
{% elseif 'attente' in statusRaw %}
    {% set statusBadge = '<span class="badge b-orange">' ~ (contrat.status ?? 'En attente') ~ '</span>' %}
{% else %}
    {% set statusBadge = '<span class="badge b-gray">' ~ (contrat.status ?? 'N/A') ~ '</span>' %}
{% endif %}

<div class="status-banner">
    <div class="status-banner-left">
        <div class="status-banner-title">{{ contrat.typeContrat ?? 'Type non défini' }}</div>
        <div class="status-banner-sub">
            {% if contrat.dateDebut and contrat.dateFin %}
                Du {{ contrat.dateDebut|date('d/m/Y') }} au {{ contrat.dateFin|date('d/m/Y') }}
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="status-banner-right">{{ statusBadge|raw }}</div>
</div>

<!-- ══ BODY ══ -->
<div class="content">

    <!-- Section 1 : Candidat -->
    <div class="section-title">Informations du Candidat</div>
    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td class="lbl">Nom complet</td>
            <td class="val">{{ meta.nom ?? '' }} {{ meta.prenom ?? '' }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="lbl">Email</td>
            <td class="val">{{ meta.email ?? '-' }}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <hr class="divider">

    <!-- Section 2 : Contrat (two columns) -->
    <div class="section-title">Détails du Contrat</div>

    <div class="two-col">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="amount">{{ contrat.salaire is not null ? contrat.salaire|number_format(0, ',', ' ') ~ ' TND' : '-' }}</div>
                <div class="amount-label">Salaire mensuel brut</div>
            </div>
            <table class="info-table" style="margin-top:10px;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="lbl">Type de contrat</td>
                    <td class="val"><span class="badge b-blue">{{ contrat.typeContrat ?? '-' }}</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="lbl">Statut</td>
                    <td class="val">{{ statusBadge|raw }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="lbl">Volume horaire</td>
                    <td class="val">{{ contrat.volumeHoraire ?? '-' }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="lbl">Période</td>
                    <td class="val">{{ contrat.getPeriode() ?? '-' }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="col">
            <table class="info-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="lbl">Date de début</td>
                    <td class="val">{{ contrat.dateDebut ? contrat.dateDebut|date('d/m/Y') : '-' }}</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="lbl">Date de fin</td>
                    <td class="val">{{ contrat.dateFin ? contrat.dateFin|date('d/m/Y') : '-' }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            {% if meta.decision_finale %}
            <table class="info-table" style="margin-top:10px;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="lbl">Décision recrutement</td>
                    <td class="val">
                        {% set ld = meta.decision_finale|lower %}
                        {% if 'accept' in ld %}<span class="badge b-green">{{ meta.decision_finale }}</span>
                        {% elseif 'refus' in ld %}<span class="badge b-red">{{ meta.decision_finale }}</span>
                        {% else %}<span class="badge b-orange">{{ meta.decision_finale }}</span>{% endif %}
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="lbl">Date de décision</td>
                    <td class="val">{{ meta.date_decision ? meta.date_decision|date('d/m/Y') : '-' }}</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
    </div>

    {% if contrat.avantages %}
    <hr class="divider">
    <div class="section-title">Avantages</div>
    <div class="text-box">{{ contrat.avantages }}</div>
    {% endif %}

    {% if meta.type_entretien %}
    <hr class="divider">
    <div class="section-title">Entretien associé</div>
    <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
            <td class="lbl">Type d'entretien</td>
            <td class="val">
                <span class="badge {{ meta.type_entretien == 'RH' ? 'b-blue' : 'b-orange' }}">{{ meta.type_entretien }}</span>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="lbl">Date de l'entretien</td>
            <td class="val">{{ meta.date_entretien ? meta.date_entretien|date('d/m/Y') : '-' }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td class="lbl">Lieu</td>
            <td class="val">{{ meta.lieu ?? '-' }}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    {% endif %}

    <hr class="divider">

    <!-- Section : Signatures -->
    <div class="section-title">Signatures</div>
    <div class="sig-section">
        <div class="sig-table">
            <div class="sig-col">
                <div class="sig-box">
                    <div class="sig-title">Le Candidat</div>
                    <div class="sig-name">{{ meta.nom ?? '' }} {{ meta.prenom ?? '' }}</div>
                    <div class="sig-role">Candidat</div>
                    <div class="sig-line">Signature &amp; Date</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sig-spacer"></div>
            <div class="sig-col">
                <div class="sig-box">
                    <div class="sig-title">VOS — Représentant RH</div>
                    <div class="sig-name">Service des Ressources Humaines</div>
                    <div class="sig-role">Virtual Onboarding System</div>
                    <div class="sig-line">Cachet &amp; Signature</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sig-notice">
            En signant ce contrat, les deux parties reconnaissent avoir pris connaissance des conditions générales
            d'emploi et s'engagent à les respecter. Ce document constitue un accord légalement contraignant.
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<!-- ══ FOOTER ══ -->
<div class="footer">
    <div class="footer-left">
        <div class="footer-brand">VOS — Virtual Onboarding System</div>
        <div>Contrat #{{ contrat.id }} — Document confidentiel et non transférable</div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-right">
        <span class="confidential">Confidentiel</span><br>
        <span style="margin-top:4px;display:inline-block;">
            Genere le {{ generatedAt|date('d/m/Y') }} a {{ generatedAt|date('H:i') }}
        </span>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
